query:
SELECT 
  br.id,
  br.branch_id,
  b.name as branch_name,
  br.week_number,
  br.month,
  br.year,
  br.total_bonus,
  br.status,
  br.start_date,
  br.end_date,
  br.created_at
FROM bonus_requests br
JOIN branches b ON br.branch_id = b.id
WHERE b.name LIKE '%طويق%'
AND br.week_number = 3
AND br.year = 2026
AND br.month = 1;
